{"type":"answer","id":107251,"parentType":"question","parentId":13459,"uid":23714,"contents":"如果你真的非常在意【安全】，最好的方法是——<b>别用手机！</b><br>\n<br>\n下面引用编程随想的一篇文章：<br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/04/Security-News.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《近期安全动态和点评（2019年1季度）》</a><br>\n<blockquote>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ◇贝佐斯的手机被入侵<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 《<a href=\"http://www.sohu.com/a/305282847_116132\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">贝索斯手机隐私遭入侵，疑为沙特政府所为 @ 搜狐</a>》<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 《<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2019/03/31/media/jeff-bezos-gavin-de-becker-saudi-arabia-leak/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Jeff Bezos investigator: Saudi Arabia obtained private information @ CNN</a>》<br>\n<br>\n　　<b>编程随想注：</b><br>\n　　作为目前的世界首富，而且还是顶级 IT 公司的老板，贝佐斯显然拥有顶级的安全顾问团队。<br>\n　　如果连他的手机都会被入侵（而且是被“深度渗透”），这说明啥捏？你自己想一下吧。</blockquote><br>\n引申阅读：<br>\n<a href=\"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/01/Security-Guide-for-Political-Activists.html#head-13\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《为啥朝廷总抓不到俺——十年反党活动的安全经验汇总》</a>","date":"2019-12-17","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}